how to import acadgild in oracle vm box:
 	  1. First open the oracle virtual box 
 	  2. And then click file in the left corner 
 	  3. In that you will see the import application click that
 	  4. You will see the browse page. browse where the acadgild file is and import it.
 	  5. It shows the drive you have choosen.
 	  6. Click next and then remove the tick in usb controller and insert click the tick mark in reinitialize the mac address.
 	  7. It will take 5 to 10 minutes to import
 	  8. And then click start to start the acadgild and type user name, password to login to linux .
 	  9. Finally Work in the oracle vm box.
 
